DTEND:20260509T170000Z
DTSTAMP:20260509T000000Z
SUMMARY:Slow Yoga with Lea Peace
DESCRIPTION:Lea Peace will direct\,\n\nSlow motion\, mindful 
 yoga\n\n\n	\n	Sitting in a chair\,\n	\n	\n	Checking in with thoughts and 
 feelings\,\n	\n	\n	Exploring intention and attention in 
 breath\,\n	\n	\n	Exploring range of motion in joints\,\n	\n	\n	Engage in a 
 bit of core strength building\,\n	\n	\n	Finish up with some standing and 
 balancing.\n	\n\n\nAbout the presenter.\n\nLea Peace has been practicing 
 yoga and meditation for over 50\nyears. Her 200-hour yoga teacher cert. is 
 from Kripalu.\n\n
LOCATION:West Orange - Community Room 1
ORGANIZER;CN="West Orange Library":MAILTO:events@westorange.bccls.org
CATEGORIES:Health & Wellness
UID:LibCal-10341-16586876
URL:https://bccls.libcal.com/event/16586876
