SUMMARY:Jazz Performance by the Ellie Lee Trio
DESCRIPTION:With Ellie Lee\n\nShe plans to play jazz standards and creative 
 creations. The harmonious blend of the two styles guarantees an enjoyable 
 listening experience.\n\nArtist information\n\nAs a pianist\, she excels in 
 all the idioms she employs\, including careful attention to the minutiae of 
 arrangement and orchestration\, a deep understanding of groove\, and 
 providing her musicians with ample opportunity to showcase their talents. 
 On top of that\, her piano skills are top-notch.
LOCATION:West Orange - Community Room 1
ORGANIZER;CN="West Orange Library":MAILTO:events@westorange.bccls.org
CATEGORIES:Performance
UID:LibCal-10341-16604563
