SUMMARY:Native Gardening: An Introduction
DESCRIPTION:with Karen Fricke\, Rutgers Master Gardeners of Essex\n\nLearn 
 about the importance and benefits of native plants and how using native 
 plants in home gardens provides the environment with connected habitats for 
 conservation.\n\nMaster Gardener Karen Fricke will give a comprehensive 
